snippet.title: MAMIYA - A Shared Illusion of the World's End - Opening Movie
snippet.description:
MAMIYA - A Shared Illusion of the World's End is releasing worldwide in Spring 2021!

Developed by Kenkou Land, localized and published by Fruitbat Factory
Translation: Conjueror, Andrew Hodgson
Editing: Garejei

Pre-order here: https://fruitbatfactory.com/mamiya
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1394930/MAMIYA/
